statements: SELECT id, symbol, price, volume, time FROM tick_data WHERE id = 1;
SELECT symbol, price, time FROM tick_data WHERE volume > 1000 ORDER BY time DESC;
SELECT id, symbol, price, volume, time FROM tick_data WHERE price < 50;
SELECT symbol, volume FROM tick_data WHERE time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM tick_data WHERE symbol LIKE 'AAPL%';
SELECT * FROM tick_data ORDER BY symbol ASC, price DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT symbol, price, volume FROM tick_data WHERE volume > 1000 ORDER BY time DESC
SELECT symbol, AVG(price) AS average_price FROM tick_data GROUP BY symbol HAVING AVG(price) > 50 ORDER BY average_price DESC
SELECT id, symbol, price FROM tick_data WHERE symbol IN ('AAPL', 'GOOGL', 'AMZN') AND price > 1000 ORDER BY id ASC
SELECT * FROM tick_data WHERE time >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND time <= '2022-12-31 23:59:59' ORDER BY time ASC
SELECT * FROM tick_data LIMIT 10;
SELECT ticker, price FROM tick_data WHERE volume > 1000;
SELECT timestamp, ticker, price FROM tick_data WHERE price > 50 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT ticker, volume FROM tick_data WHERE ticker IN ('AAPL', 'GOOGL', 'MSFT');
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name FROM strategy_data WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM tick_data WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT ticker, price FROM tick_data WHERE volume > 1000 AND ticker = 'AAPL';
SELECT MIN(price), MAX(price), AVG(volume) FROM tick_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name FROM strategy_data WHERE start_date < '2021-06-01' ORDER BY strategy_id ASC;
SELECT ticker, COUNT(DISTINCT(price)) AS unique_prices FROM tick_data GROUP BY ticker HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT(price)) > 5;
SELECT * FROM tick_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT ticker_symbol, price FROM tick_data WHERE volume > 100 ORDER BY price ASC
SELECT ticker_symbol, timestamp, volume FROM tick_data WHERE price > 50.00 AND volume < 500 ORDER BY timestamp
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name FROM strategy WHERE LENGTH(strategy_name) > 10 ORDER BY strategy_id
SELECT trade_id, timestamp, price FROM trade_history WHERE volume > 200 ORDER BY timestamp
SELECT ticker_symbol, timestamp, price FROM tick_data WHERE price > 100
SELECT * FROM strategy WHERE strategy_name LIKE 'Trend%'
SELECT ticker_symbol, timestamp, price FROM tick_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT MAX(price) AS max_price, MIN(price) AS min_price FROM tick_data
SELECT ticker_symbol, COUNT(*) AS trade_count FROM trade_history GROUP BY ticker_symbol HAVING COUNT(*) > 5
SELECT * FROM ticks_data WHERE ticker_symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT price, volume FROM ticks_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT trader_name, strategy FROM traders WHERE strategy = 'Quantitative';
SELECT * FROM trades_history WHERE action = 'BUY' ORDER BY trade_time DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, description FROM strategies;
SELECT * FROM ticks_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT ticker_symbol, price, volume FROM ticks_data WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT t.trader_name, th.action, th.price FROM traders t JOIN trades_history th ON t.trader_id = th.trader_id WHERE th.price > 500 ORDER BY th.price DESC;
SELECT th.trader_id, COUNT(th.trade_id) AS total_trades FROM trades_history th GROUP BY th.trader_id HAVING total_trades > 5 ORDER BY total_trades DESC;

SELECT s.strategy_name, s.description, COUNT(th.trade_id) AS total_trades FROM strategies s LEFT JOIN trades_history th ON s.strategy_id = th.trader_id WHERE th.price < 1000 GROUP BY s.strategy_name, s.description ORDER BY total_trades DESC;
SELECT * FROM tick_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT ticker_symbol, price, timestamp FROM tick_data WHERE volume > 10000 ORDER BY price ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name, author FROM strategy_data WHERE author = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM trade_data WHERE quantity > 100 AND price < 50 ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT account_id, account_name, balance, currency FROM account_data ORDER BY balance DESC LIMIT 7;
SELECT * FROM tick_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT ticker_symbol, price FROM tick_data WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT trade_id, quantity, price FROM trade_data WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY quantity ASC, price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT account_name, balance FROM account_data WHERE currency = 'USD' ORDER BY balance DESC, account_name;
SELECT strategy_name, author FROM strategy_data ORDER BY strategy_name;
